data.description: Welcome home to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home for sale! This meticulously maintained property boasts a spacious layout, perfect for comfortable living and entertaining. Impeccably updated and meticulously maintained, this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers a perfect blend of modern comfort and timeless charm. Kitchen features stainless steel appliances that elevate the kitchen's functionally and style. Step into the thoughtfully renovated bathrooms, where every detail has been carefully considered to provide both luxury and convenience. Step outside to discover a beautiful back patio, ideal for enjoying al fresco dining or simply unwinding in the serene outdoor oasis. With it's inviting atmosphere and thoughtful upgrades throughout, this home is a true gem waiting to welcome its next lucky owner.
